data.content:
noun
the Dark Ages :the period of European history from about A.D. 500 to 1000 :the first 500 years of the Middle Ages
the Dark Ages or the dark ages often humorous :the period of time before things developed into their modern form
In the dark ages before computers, we often wrote our letters by hand.
Her father's ideas about women are from the Dark Ages.

the Dark Ages
thời kỳ hậu đế chế La Mã (ở Châu Âu), thời kỳ đen tối (coi như không có gì về văn học nghệ thuật)
